{
  "texts": [
    "Traditional LLMs utilize sophisticated neural network architectures, such as Transformers described earlier, which enable them to capture complex patterns and dependencies in language.",
    "The training objective is to optimize the model's parameters to maximize the likelihood of generating the correct next word in a given context.",
    "The context depends highly on the occurrence of the same words in a specific sequence in the past (now part of training data).",
    "So new instances for context will not work.",
    "With strategic prompt design based, we can ensure that the context is always accurate and therefore have more control on the outcome."
  ]
}